            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36016479">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">许多优秀的研究成果，着眼于与复仇相关的惩罚问题，这等于说，制裁肯定是合法的、公正的、不偏不移的

“While there are many excellent studies of its legitimate cousin, retribution – that is to say, the legal and supposedly impartial exercise of justice – there is no general study of the role that vengeance played in the aftermath of the war.”

这段的翻译完全就……错了。

真正意思是

尽管很多...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-08-31 09:56</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>许多优秀的研究成果，着眼于与复仇相关的惩罚问题，这等于说，制裁肯定是合法的、公正的、不偏不移的</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>“While there are many excellent studies of its legitimate cousin, retribution – that is to say, the legal and supposedly impartial exercise of justice – there is no general study of the role that vengeance played in the aftermath of the war.”<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>这段的翻译完全就……错了。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>真正意思是<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>尽管很多研究着重于报复的合法表亲“惩罚”——也就是合乎法律、被认为是无私执行法律的行为——但对报复在战后扮演的角色，却缺乏整体研究。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







